難度很高，但經過李孝利傳授秘訣後，IU很快便上手，她今日更在自己的Instagram上傳與李孝利一起玩瑜伽的視頻，IU竟然可以跟玩了多年瑜伽的李孝利一樣，完成高難度的動作，令她本人也非常滿意，故忍不住要上傳短片跟大家分享她的成果。"},{"pid":"db69132a6e468698842fb14de5c5438d6e5f9fae","tid":358112,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T13:26:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DHHH1oHVoAAS6zg.jpg:large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDHHH1oHVoAAS6zg.jpg%3Alarge&h=94965b3c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"472f951597aaf563e58fe4cbb5f30c5f73dc6ddc","tid":358112,"uid":35014,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T13:26:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fe62a20df5f80ee51699b5f43ac65c4251c3cea8","tid":358112,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T13:32:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://ww4.sinaimg.cn/large/005MHWLRgy1fii2doaikqg30d109ax6q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fww4.sinaimg.cn%2Flarge%2F005MHWLRgy1fii2doaikqg30d109ax6q.jpg&h=eecd8bb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原來iu都會柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83ba4183a96b20f7b356367035b80d3eb23d4cb5","tid":358112,"uid":91096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T13:34:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>現年24歲的韓國女歌手IU與38歲女星李孝利雖然年齡相差14歲，但因二人同樣熱愛音樂，自從IU以民宿職員身份錄影李孝利兩公婆主持的綜藝節目《孝利家的民宿》後，二人很快便成了很好的朋友。<br />\n<br />\n李孝利更以大姐姐的身份給了IU不少寶貴意見，而且她還在節目中教IU做瑜伽。原本IU亦表示瑜伽的動作難度很高，但經過李孝利傳授秘訣後，IU很快便上手，她今日更在自己的Instagram上傳與李孝利一起玩瑜伽的視頻，IU竟然可以跟玩了多年瑜伽的李孝利一樣，完成高難度的動作，令她本人也非常滿意，故忍不住要上傳短片跟大家分享她的成果。</blockquote><br />\n呢個唔算高難度  李孝利話係入門級"},{"pid":"e3ce754c5dfd801406f30e221ad9871ada1dbe48","tid":358112,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T14:03:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://ww4.sinaimg.cn/large/005MHWLRgy1fii2doaikqg30d109ax6q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fww4.sinaimg.cn%2Flarge%2F005MHWLRgy1fii2doaikqg30d109ax6q